title: Looking for a group or team to play with
body:
Plat V, prefer people who discord/skype.
I played casually, competitively, ranked, aram, whatever. Enjoy Twisted Treeline too.
Msg here or add me in-game 69er

replies.body: hey man add me in game I'm creating a team for that new up coming weekend event games. feel free to add and ill add you to the club, I wanted about 15 people in it because me being from NSW I struggle to get 4 other people ready to play when I am,
Hey 69er, if you are looking for a league group to join I am growing our league sector of our community if you would like to join us at https://discord.gg/VPzyWYp
I'm trash and a supp main but feel free to add me I'm always inviting people for 5 mans.
